title: 383E.01 COMMISSIONERS' SALARIES.
text: Notwithstanding the provisions of any general law enacted prior to May 18, 1967, to the contrary, whether effective before or after this section or section 383E.02, the yearly salaries of each of the members of the board of county commissioners of Anoka County shall be set by said board and shall be payable in equal installments at least once monthly.
